column1: 2011 APA Apollon Open Summer Iron Bash - Edison, New Jersey
Gear Equipped Best Lifter: Mike Romeo
Raw Drug Tested Best Lifter: Matt Arnold
Non Tested Best Lifter: Tim Gale
Push-Pull DT Best Lifter: Aaron Landy
Push-Pull NT Best Lifter: Jason Fruge
Deadlift Only Best Lifter: John Wojciechowski
Bench Only Best Lifter: Jason Manenkoff
1st Place Team: Skiba's Competition Barbell Club
The 2011 APA Apollon Summer Iron Bash drew 50 competitors with the majority competing in the Raw Categories. Our next event in Edison is scheduled for December 10, 2011 and
we already have around 80 competitors committed to competing in that event. By the time the meet comes around we very well may end up with 100+ competitors in that event.
The event was computerized and projected on a screen so all spectators and competitors knew their placement/score/order throughout the entire day.
A very special thanks to Henry Skiba and crew, Big Tony, Robert Samborsky, our referees, spotters & loaders, and of course the lifters for making this an outstanding and memorable event.
Thank you everybody for an outstaning event!
